contentrichtext.text: There are several distinctions and recognitions known as the '''Eagle Award.''' *Eagle Award, the highest rank of the [[Zambia Scouts Association]] *Eagle Award, the highest award given to a civilian by the [[National Guard of the United States]] *Eagle Award, an award given by the [[International Air Transport Association]] to airports or other aviation bodies. *[[Eagle Award (comics)]], an annual set of comic book awards ==See also== *[[Eagle Scout (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}}
